description: The Sabrent NT-USBC Ethernet Adapter offers the most convenient and efficient way to connect with a laptop or desktop computer to an Ethernet network, and makes the connection as easy by plugging one end of the cable into the RJ45 receptacle of the Ethernet Adapter and the other end into one port of the supporting hub.System features:* Supports 10Mb/s and 100Mb/s N-way, Auto-Negotiation operation.* Full-Speed (480Mb/s) USB devices.* Supports all USB standard command.* Supports TCIP/IP, NetBEUI, IPX/SPX protocols.* Supports suspend/resume detection logic.Supported Operating Systems include:Windows 8 (64bit), Windows 8 (32bit), Windows 7 (64bit), Windows 7 (32bit), Windows Vista (64bit), Windows Vista (32bit), Windows XP (32bit)/ Mac OS XWhats in the box?* USB 2.0 LAN Ethernet adapter
title: Sabrent USB 2.0 to 10/100 Fast Ethernet LAN Wired Network Adapter for Macbook, Chromebook, Windows 8 and Earlier, Surface Pro, Linux, and Specific Android Tablets (ASIX AX88772 chipset) NT-USBC
